name: Immune U
summary: Shrink down. Shoot viruses. Save the world. Immune U is a race against time to destroy viruses and collect their precious RNA samples to help save the world one virus at a time. Shrink down into a patient’s stomach where the infection is greatest shooting all the virus you can in the time remaining for the shrinking effect. Gaining score as you destroy these viruses and obtaining their RNA, adding up to your total score displayed in the lab for all your friends to see. Get out there and kill some viruses.
